\pard\fi720\li720\sa160\sl259\slmult0\b\f0\fs40\lang9 PROJECT Autonomous Drone Navigation\par

\pard\fi720\li2880\sa160\sl259\slmult0\b0\fs28 END USER MANUAL\par

\pard\sa160\sl259\slmult0\b Project Description:-\par
\b0\fs22 This project focuses on developing an advanced Autonomous Drone Navigation System. Students will engage in creating a sophisticated flight computer, capable of interpreting depth images from lidar and Zed stereoscopic camera. This system will empower the drone to learn about its surrounding environment and formulate a flight path independent of GPS data.\par
\b\fs28 Project Hardware requirements:-\par
\b0\fs22 Drone, Zed 2 camera , 2D lidar , Jetson nano , Pixhawk\par
\b\fs28 Project Software requirements:\par
\b0\fs22 Visual Studio Code, Zed SDK, ROS(Robot Operating System), Unreal engine, Q Ground Control\par
\b\fs28 Installations:\par
\fs24 ZED SDK Installation \par
\fs22 Prerequisites:\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent360{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa160\sl259\slmult0\b0 A compatible ZED stereo camera.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Ensure your system meets the minimum hardware requirements specified by Stereolabs.\par

\pard\sa160\sl259\slmult0\b Installation Steps\b0\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent360{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa160\sl259\slmult0 Download the SDK: Go to the ZED SDK download page and download the latest version compatible with your Windows system.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Run the Installer: Execute the downloaded .exe file and follow the on-screen instructions. This will install the necessary drivers and the SDK.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Restart Your Computer: After installation, reboot your computer to ensure all drivers are properly loaded.\par

\pard\sa160\sl259\slmult0\par
\b\fs24 Unreal Engine Setup \par
\fs22 Prerequisites:\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent360{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li765\sa160\sl259\slmult0\b0 A PC with Windows 10/11, macOS, or Linux.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Adequate hardware specs to run the engine smoothly (refer to Unreal Engine\rquote s system requirements).\par
