\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent360{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa160\sl259\slmult0\b0 Download Epic Games Launcher: Visit the Epic Games Download Page and download the Epic Games Launcher.\par
