\fs22 Prerequisites :\b0\par

\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent360{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa160\sl259\slmult0 A compatible computer\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}A UAV that communicates using the MAVLink protocol.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}A stable internet connection for downloading the software.\par

