{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Install the Application:\par

\pard\li720\sa160\sl259\slmult0 -Windows: Run the downloaded .exe installer and follow the installation prompts.\par
-macOS: Open the .dmg file and drag the QGroundControl app to your Applications folder\par

