\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent360{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa160\sl259\slmult0\b0 Connect to Your UAV: Connect your UAV to QGroundControl using USB, Telemetry Radio, or Wi-Fi, depending on your drone's setup.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Firmware Setup: If needed, update your UAV's firmware through QGroundControl.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Calibrate Sensors: Follow the on-screen instructions in QGroundControl to calibrate your UAV's sensors.\par

