\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent360{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa160\sl259\slmult0\b0\fs24 Primarily a machine with Ubuntu 20.04 (Focal) release or Windows 10/11\b\par
