3 other ways to use\par
1. ultra_simple: An ultra-simple command line application demonstrates the simplest way to\par
connect to an RPLIDAR device and continuously fetching the scan data and\par
outputting the data to the console.\par
2. simple_grabber:\par
A command line grab application. Each execution will grab two round of laser\par
